{"tid":734822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習權時代】用激光槍鎮壓示威者 強國警新裝備惹恐慌","createTime":"2018-07-09T03:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:25:07.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c82f41e2b0a725679a8e7b6d71ffc03a1e98d5f4","tid":734822,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:43:06.000Z","msg":"【習權時代】用激光槍鎮壓示威者 強國警新裝備惹恐慌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180708/58415732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180708%2F58415732&d=qeQ5DQznnouuRGWXlpqzrozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=626bd569\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180708%2F58415732&h=bbd17e09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180708/58415732</a><br />\n<br />\n隨身攜帶的激光槍，並非科幻電影橋段！四川成都的一家公司早前開發出警用激光步槍，射程800米，並可連續發射激光1,000次，據稱可遠程燒毀橫額，如果被攻擊對像身穿易燃布料，更可能全身都會被點燃。中國訪民對這款新式武器感到恐慌，擔心在維權活動中傷害。<br />\n<br />\n據海內外媒體報道，該款由成都恆安警用裝備製造公司生產的激光步槍，將裝備中國武警反恐部隊。開發者披露，激光步槍主要用於特殊情況，例如用激光引燃抗議活動中的「非法橫額」，或者灼傷抗議者的頭髮或衣服。<span style=\"color: red;\">「由於其激光的發射過程肉眼看不到，也不產生任何聲音。被攻擊者很難察覺攻擊來自何處，看似意外受傷」。不過，開發者稱，這款武器並不致命，也不能讓人體的皮膚「瞬間碳化」。<br />\n</span><br />\n在四川論壇，有網民炮轟這些發明被用於對付示威者，<span style=\"color: red;\">「這兩天炒作得厲害，美國國防部都驚呆了的超級武器，原來是這個」。</span><span style=\"color: red;\">攀枝花市一網民稱，激光槍可以燒毀拆遷戶、釘子戶屋頂的五星紅旗。</span><br />\n<br />\n黑龍江訪民王女士更指，激光槍製造者聲稱激光槍將裝備武警部隊，新武器明顯是為了鎮壓民眾，「這款槍就是用於維穩，鎮壓老百姓。為了政權，他們甚麼辦法都想到了，想絕了。激光本身對人體是會有後遺症的傷害。而且違反聯合國人權宣言。在他們眼中，權力大於一切法律。如果影響了我的權力，我會想盡一切辦法去鎮壓」。<br />\n<br />\n北京維權人士倪玉蘭批評，有關當局用先進的激光武器對付民眾。她認為，聯合國人權理事會及人權組織應關注此事。有研究人員表示，ZKZM-500 型激光槍單價為10萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台"},{"pid":"b25b66b33eb82f634a19e00f941c7e3c00d82cae","tid":734822,"uid":57376,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:49:12.000Z","msg":"吹到咁大，有片睇未先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n800米？無擴散？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面用緊咩電池？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bf898a51c5a74e43b145dc1776e64b894acc8e","tid":734822,"uid":51701,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/115044_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F115044_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=87b85812&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc6bee18d737b08531932a2d1c2d67c1d21cdcda","tid":734822,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1db422101062d2d2aed93bc85405b15adfda2d","tid":734822,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:53:19.000Z","msg":"射盲你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efca9dfc9d5c3ed6a0a91ff1525b5283a22e72a","tid":734822,"uid":511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"55bf898a51c5a74e43b145dc1776e64b894acc8e","tid":734822,"uid":51701,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/115044_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F115044_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=87b85812&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38348357003c7998c654e581523f35a51ea61cae","tid":734822,"uid":144035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32340c28727a8473d2457e704f8591d0a9c1